@using Postal
@model Inview.Epi.EpiFund.Web.Models.Emails.ConfirmationToBuyerInsQuoteOrderedEmail
To: @Model.To
From: USCREonline <info@uscreonline.com>
Subject: @Model.Subject
Content-type: text/html;charset=utf-8
<html>
<body>
<p><img src="http://uscreonline.com/content/images/uscrelogowithbg.png" /></p>
    <table style="width: 100%;">
        <tr>
            <td align="left">To @Model.BuyerName</td>
            <td align="right">@Model.Date.ToString("MMMM d, yyyy")</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <p><b style="color:darkgoldenrod">US CRE Online.com</b> P&C Insurance Quote Order confirmation:</p>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <td width="80"></td>
            <td>
                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Ins. Underwriter:</td>
                        <td>@Model.CompanyName</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Asset ID&#35;:</td>
                        <td>@Model.AssetId</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Property Address:</td>
                        <td>@Model.AssetAddress1 @Model.AssetAddress2, @Model.AssetCity, @Model.AssetState @Model.AssetZip</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Property Type:</td>
                        <td>@Model.AssetDescription</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>APN:</td>
                        <td>@Model.APN</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>PI-B Vesting Entity:</td>
                        <td>@Model.VestingEntity</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <p>
        The above captioned Insurance Underwriter has agreed with USCREonline.com LLC "USC" on behalf of its registered members to secure
        and upload a Property & Casualty Insurance Coverage Quote for the above captioned data file at www.USCREonline.com.  Per USC automated
        order, @Model.CompanyName shall endeavor to secure and upload the P&C Insurance Quote for the above captioned commercial investment 
        property in the ensuing business days.  Note:  USC Registrant&#39;s are not required/obligated to employ the services of @Model.CompanyName for 
        any purpose (present or future).  There is no cost to you for this Document upload service to the respective USC Asset File.
    </p>
    <p>
        When the Quote is secured and uploaded to the file, you will receive an automated e mail notification thereto.  Note:  all documents will be
        uploaded in Adobe Acrobat PDF non-editable Format.  Note: @Model.CompanyName shall only have access to upload the defined Insurance 
        Quote to the subject File.  Upon completion of such upload, no further access to the Asset File from @Model.CompanyName is possible.  The
        Asset File remains fully secure at all times.  Upon your receipt of the USC automated e mail notification that the Insurance Quote has been 
        uploaded, you will be encouraged to review said Quote for your consideration.  
    </p>
    <p>
        Uploaded Document Review Instructions: 
    </p>
    <ol>
        <li>Go to http://www.uscreonline.com and log in.</li>
        <li>From your &#91;&#34;<b style="color:blue">My USC Page</b>&#34;&#93; &#60;click&#62; on to the &#91;<b style="color:blue">Manage Assets</b>&#93; hyperlink.</li>
        <li>
            &#60;Click&#62; the &#91;Asset #&#93; that matches the Asset ID# captioned above.  You will have access to the View Asset page for the Asset 
            File and have access to the DOCUMENT upload page for the limited function of uploading your respective P&C Quote.
        </li>
        <li>At the DOCUMENT upload page, &#60;Click&#62; the &#91;○ Data Available&#93; button for the respective Insurance Quote upload:</li>
        <li>
            At completion of your Document Upload, &#60;Click&#62; the &#91;Save and Submit&#93; blue button.
        </li>
        <li>After you have completed Document Uploads for subject Asset ID, press the &#91;F5&#93; keyboard key to refresh your USC page.</li>
    </ol>
    <p>
        Upon uploading the subject Document to USC, you will receive a courtesy Thank You e mail from USC. The @Model.CompanyName "My USC Page" Record of Uploaded Documents TAB shall then be automatically updated for your records.
    </p>
    <p>
        Thank you for being a valued Registrant and Customer of <i><b style="color:darkgoldenrod">United States Commercial Real Estate Online, LLC</b></i>.  It is our honor and privilege to 
        provide the defined CRE Data Portal Services to the investment community.
    </p>
    <span>The Professional Staff</span><br />
    <span><b style="color:darkgoldenrod"><i>US CRE Online, LLC</i></b></span>
</body>
</html>